local reactor = GetPartFromPort(1, "Reactor")
local dispenser = GetPartFromPort(2, "Dispenser")

while wait() do
	local fuel = reactor:GetFuel()
	for i = 1, #fuel do
		if fuel[i] <= 0 then
			dispenser:Trigger()
			wait(1)
			dispenser:Trigger()
		end
	end
end
